description: ELVEN is the second full-scale NFT project from acclaimed young artist Yasmeen Suleiman. ELVEN Launched on Yasmeen's 13th birthday in September 2021 and sold out in 6 days. ELVEN evolved in September 2022 with 100% of the assets being redrawn and all 6000 ELVEN growing up.
